  "title": "GridStatus IESO Forecast Surplus Baseload Generation",
  "description": "Report on surplus baseload generation (SBG) in Ontario by IESO. \n\nSBG occurs when electricity production from baseload facilities is greater than Ontario demand. Baseload is comprised of available nuclear, must-run hydro, self-scheduling, commissioning, intermittent, and variable generators. \n\nPublished once per day by 5PM EST.\n\nMore information [here](https://www.ieso.ca/-/media/Files/IESO/uploaded/SBG/SurplusBaseloadGen_h3.pdf)",
